## Ingredients

* 400g Mushrooms
* 100g Breadcrumbs (Panko recommended)
* 2 Cloves of Garlic
* 1 Tablespoon of Olive Oil 

## Instructions

Slice the garlic and mushrooms. Set the mushrooms aside.

Fry the garlic in olive oil until golden

- Fry 2 sliced garlic cloves in olive oil until golden
- Add 400g sliced mushrooms and fry until liquid has evaporated
- Add flour to form a roux then add milk slowly to make a b√©chamel sauce
